# Data Layer Architecture (v2.1)

**Agent rules:** `doc/ARCHITECTURE_V2_AGENT_RULES.md` §10

## PostgreSQL (single database engine)

- Migrations: `database/migrations/NNN_name.sql` (lexicographic order)
- Tenant tables: `tenant_id` + indexes; soft delete via `deleted_at` + `deleted_by`
- Multi-step writes: `withTransaction()` from `backend/src/db/pool.ts`
- Idempotent where possible; never drop columns/tables without explicit plan
- **Never** add SQLite migrations or schema for new features

## v2 Schema (launch scope)

- `accounting_periods.status` includes `locked`
- `document_metadata` (R2 `storage_key`) — no new inline BLOB columns
- `sync_queue` + `change_log` (LWW sync via `recordDomainMutation()`)
- `analytics_snapshots` (dashboard KPIs)

## Shared Packages (edit source, not copies)

| Source | Generated (do not edit) |
|--------|-------------------------|
| `shared/financial-core/` | `backend/src/financial/` |
| `shared/report-engines/` | `backend/dist/*.mjs` (transitional) |
| `shared/rbac/permissions.ts` | `backend/src/auth/permissions.ts` |

After edits: `npm run build:backend`

## Financial Reporting

All statement calculations in `shared/financial-core/` or `shared/report-engines/` only — never in components, routes, or repositories.

## New Report Checklist

1. Engine in `shared/report-engines/` (no React imports)
2. Re-export shim in `components/reports/` if UI needs old path
3. Backend `*ReportService.ts` + route under `/api/v1/reports/` with RBAC
4. Custom reports: extend `modules/reporting/`

## Legacy SQLite (deprecated — do not extend)

| Component | Location |
|-----------|----------|
| Local schema | `services/database/schema.ts` |
| Schema extraction | `npm run electron:extract-schema` |
| SQLite bridge | `electron/sqliteBridge.cjs` |
| SQLite sync | `services/database/schemaSync.ts` |
